             <a class="answer-user-name" href="//wenda.toutiao.com/user/?uid=5870111044" target="_blank" onmousedown="ba_event(&quot;Visit_Profile&quot;,&quot;From_Answer&quot;)"> 多么痛的领悟69434859 </a> 
             <a class="answer-user-tag">02-01 19:47</a> 
             <div data-node="like" class="answer-like " onclick="window.wendaDigg.bind(this)('6382105143709532417')"> 
              <i class="y-icon icon-digg"></i>
              <span data-node="like-count">51</span>赞 
